headline: How Tech Firms Are Enforcing AI Use

headline: OpenAI clinches $840 billion valuation with new funding from Amazon, Nvidia, SoftBank
summary: OpenAI's latest funding round valued the ChatGPT maker at $840 billion as Big Tech piled into the $110 billion blockbuster round, signaling the AI investment race is alive and well despite recent fears of a valuation bubble.  The funding ‌round - one of the largest private capital raises on record - includes a $30 billion investment from SoftBank, $30 billion from Nvidia, and $50 billion ‌from Amazon.
